Sentencas: Samples of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)(0.99)(ZnO)(0.01) (0 <= x <= 0.2) were synthesized by EDTA-citrate complexing, method.
Titulo: Properties of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)0.99(ZnO)0.01 Electrolyte Prepared by EDTA-citrate Complexing Method

Sentencas: The samples were characterized by thermogravimetric, X-ray diffraction, thermal expansion measurement and AC impedance spectroscope, respectively.
Titulo: Properties of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)0.99(ZnO)0.01 Electrolyte Prepared by EDTA-citrate Complexing Method

Sentencas: The effect of Y/Nd dopant ratio on the electrical properties of materials was studied particularly.
Titulo: Properties of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)0.99(ZnO)0.01 Electrolyte Prepared by EDTA-citrate Complexing Method

Sentencas: The results show that all samples prepared by EDTA-citrate complexing method have single cubic fluorite structure.
Titulo: Properties of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)0.99(ZnO)0.01 Electrolyte Prepared by EDTA-citrate Complexing Method

Sentencas: The relatively dense (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)(0.99)(ZnO)(0.01) series samples can be obtained after sintered at 1350 degrees C with 1 mol% ZnO. Among all the samples, (Ce0.8Y0.05Nd0.15O1.9)(0.99)(ZnO)(0.01) shows the highest ionic conductivity of 58.79 mS/cm measured at 750 degrees C.
Titulo: Properties of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)0.99(ZnO)0.01 Electrolyte Prepared by EDTA-citrate Complexing Method

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficients of all samples are in the range of (11.83-12.30)
Titulo: Properties of (Ce0.8Y0.2-xNdxO1.9)0.99(ZnO)0.01 Electrolyte Prepared by EDTA-citrate Complexing Method
